Package org.eolang.jeo.representation.bytecode

Contains classes for generating bytecode in the form of Java classes. Some sort of API for generating Java classes. Usefull for generating inputs for tests. The classes also used in org.eolang.jeo.representation.xmir package to generate bytecode from XMIR files.
Since:
0.1.0
